    <h1>[02-A] SOLOVERSE - CRAZY 8’s “UTTER CHAOS”</h1>
    <div class="meta-tag">[Game Rulebook] • Ages 7+ • 3-10 Players</div>

    <!-- INDEX JUMP MATRIX -->
